[Student "S"]
{NORTH opens 2\C.

SOUTH should just respond 2NT, even with 11 points. The idea is to make a positive response (which forces 
the partnership to game level), and show extra strength later.

This time there is no need. NORTH should bid 4\C (Gerber), and SOUTH answers 4\S for 
two Aces.

Next NORTH should ask for Kings, and when SOUTH shows one King NORTH should bid 7NT.}

